libraries.name: BSEC Software Library
libraries.author: Bosch Sensortec
libraries.sentence: Bosch Sensortec Environmental Cluster (BSEC) Software library
libraries.paragraph: for use with the BME680 has been conceptualized to provide higher-level signal processing and fusion for the BME680. The library receives compensated sensor values from the sensor API. It processes the BME680 signals to provide the requested sensor outputs.
